/*--------------------------------------------------------------
 *  This is a headless adaptation from the Inventor Mentor,
 *  chapter 6, example 3.
 *
 *  This example renders beveled text with complex materials.
 *  Uses embedded ProFont for reliable headless rendering.
 *------------------------------------------------------------*/

